      "2070:486": {
        "inputs": {
          "text": "Style: cinematic\n\nA teacher stands near a blackboard displaying \"LTX-2.3,\" looking directly at the viewer. She begins to walk across the classroom, her movements fluid and graceful. As she walks, she speaks in a cheerful, friendly voice, \"The kids don't know it, but I will not call to class today. I am too busy playing around with LTX 2 point 3.\" She continues walking towards the window, observing children playing outside. \"They are playing around. So will I,\" she says with a playful smile. The scene is rendered with high detail and realism, capturing the warmth and light of a sunny day.",
